intro.goal: üåçThe goal of this game is to craft as many items as possible with the 7 items provided in the hexagons. This gamemode has a daily mode, as well as an unlimited mode paired with a editor. By completing the daily mode, you can build up a win-streak. By playing unlimited, you get to learn how to play the game, learn recipes better, and play games that other players created using the editor!
intro.entering_items: üåçTo begin playing, select an item in the hexagons and then click a slot in the crafting table grid, where clicking multiple slots will "paint" these slots. Repeat this process until you see the desired recipe in the output slot. Then, click the resulting item to craft! Alternatively, you can also drag-and-drop items from the hexagon or from one slot to another. Additionally, you could also be a "Keyboard Wizard" and select the hexagons with the number keys, WASD for the crafting table slots, Space to place, and Enter to craft. Keybinds can be configured in the settings located to the left of the MCdle title.

tips.title: üåçTips
tips.individual_results_only: üåçThe game only counts individual results, not individual recipes. E.g. Both bamboo and planks make sticks, but once you crafted sticks, that's it!
tips.where_help: üåçUse the hint system if you are stuck. The wiki is a great pair for that, just search for the item you are missing!
tips.not_all_recipes: üåçCrafting Bee does not contain every craftable recipe. Only standard shaped and shapeless recipes inside the crafting table are included. Non standard recipes, like custom fireworks, decorated pots, or similar are not included.
